t"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/milano-teatro-alla-scala-falstaff/#comments">2 Replies</a></div><div class="entry-share"> <span style="color: #363636">Share This<i class="icon-plus"></i></span><div class="entry-share-icons"> <span class="ct-pinterest" title="Share on Pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/milano-teatro-alla-scala-falstaff/&amp;media=http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/01/112_IMG_7834-1024x682.jpg&amp;description=Milano,%20Teatro%20alla%20Scala:%20&#8220;Falstaff&#8221;" target="_blank"><i class="icon-pinterest"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-fb" title="Share on Facebook"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/sharer.php?u=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/milano-teatro-alla-scala-falstaff/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-facebook"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-twitter" title="Share on Twitter"><a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?text=Milano,%20Teatro%20alla%20Scala:%20&#8220;Falstaff&#8221;&amp;url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/milano-teatro-alla-scala-falstaff/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-twitter"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-gplus" title="Share on Google Plus"><a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2013/01/milano-teatro-alla-scala-falstaff/" target="_blank"><i class="icon-google-plus"></i></a></span></div></div></div><footer class="entry-meta single-meta clearfix"><div class="entry-date updated"> <span class="date-month">Gen</span> <span class="date-day">23</span><meta itemprop="datePublished" content="Gen 23, 2013"></div> /* */<span class="meta-category" title="Category"> <i class="icon-tag"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/archives/category/recensioni/" >Opera</a> </span> <span class="meta-author" title="Author"> <i class="icon-user"></i> <span class="author vcard"><a class="url fn n" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/andrea-dellabianca/" title="View all posts by Andrea Dellabianca" rel="author">Andrea Dellabianca</a></span> </span